      <p class="font-semibold text-white mb-1">Offload windows follow the event schedule — see the <a href="/schedule" class="text-furdu-teal hover:underline">Schedule</a> for exact times per day.</p>
      <p class="text-furdu-muted">After offloading, the ConOps workstation syncs automatically to the Nextcloud server for Reo (Philippines) to access in near real-time.</p>
